=== extrapolation 估算真 SQLite latency (better-sqlite3 sync API) ===
实测 pure JS in-memory 已 baseline,真 SQLite 额外加:
- SELECT 全表: ~0.001-0.005ms/row (better-sqlite3 row mode 10k = ~10-50ms)
- JSON.parse 每 row: ~0.001ms (10k row = ~10ms)
- UPDATE 命中部分: ~0.05-0.1ms/UPDATE (typical 10 deletedIds 触发几个 UPDATE)
- tx commit overhead: ~5-10ms

真 SQLite 估算 latency for typical case (N=10000, deletedIds=10):
  SELECT 10k = ~30ms + parse 10k = ~10ms + UPDATE 几次 = ~1ms + tx ~5ms ≈ 50ms
真 SQLite 估算 latency for stress case (N=100000, deletedIds=10):
  SELECT 100k = ~300ms + parse 100k = ~100ms + UPDATE 几次 = ~1ms + tx ~5ms ≈ 400ms

